  <brief_title>A Study of Patupilone in Patients With Advanced Solid Tumors and Varying Degrees of Hepatic Function</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-label, Phase I Study to Evaluate the Safety, Tolerability, and Pharmacokinetics of Patupilone in Patients With Advanced Solid Tumors and Varying Degrees of Hepatic Function</official_title>
